name: Bikes, Beards And Babes
description:
At Cafe Culture we take pride in our product, so each t-shirts is 100% cotton and hand tailored in the UK to give a slim fit. Each one is also individually digitally printed in the UK to give the best possible print quality with a soft handle. Due to the nature of our product we ask that you allow five working days for delivery.

Model is wearing a size large.

Weight: 150gm/m² 
Fabric: 100% Cotton 
Available in: White
